title: New Season, New Home! Our Beautiful 2Bed/2Bath Available, Call Now!
posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath', 'Say hello to Bear Valley Park, a mecca for fun and adventure with a twist of modern comfort.', 'Our Denver, CO, apartments for rent sit in the center of an unbeatable location – close to scenic hiking and biking trails and just minutes from all your daily needs.', 'Garden-style grounds welcome you home each day, while phenomenal features and community amenities allow for a life of style and ease.', 'Let us be the first to welcome you to the Southwest Bear Valley Park neighborhood.', 'Features:', 'Vaulted Ceilings*, Spacious Private Balcony or Patio, Gas Fireplace*, Dishwasher, Walk-In Closets*, In-Home Washer & Dryer, Kitchen Islands*, Refrigerator with Ice Maker, Air Conditioning, Microwave, Stainless-Steel Appliances', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities:', 'Bark Park, Onsite Maintenance, 24-Hour Fitness Center, Heated Swimming Pool, Business Center, Clubhouse, Great Location Off Highway 285, Outdoor Fire Pit, Parking Lot with Available Garages, Easy Access to Hiking & Biking Trails, Community BBQ Grills', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', '3JeoMz9KCI']
